558
00:43:02,160 --> 00:43:03,310
Hey.

559
00:43:03,310 --> 00:43:04,400
Stop taking photos.

560
00:43:26,960 --> 00:43:28,530
I like your smell.

561
00:43:30,400 --> 00:43:31,500
