593
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:47,960
I can't even worry about you getting hurt.

594
00:45:48,430 --> 00:45:49,630
So stay out of it.

595
00:45:50,330 --> 00:45:51,330
That monster...

596
00:45:51,900 --> 00:45:53,530
is out of your league.

597
00:45:55,530 --> 00:45:56,630
Have you...

598
00:45:57,900 --> 00:45:59,260
killed someone?

599
00:46:04,960 --> 00:46:06,230
