603
00:46:22,200 --> 00:46:23,300
A monster?

604
00:46:25,360 --> 00:46:26,530
Who's the real monster?

605
00:46:28,730 --> 00:46:29,830
I am.

606
00:46:30,730 --> 00:46:31,830
Can you say...

607
00:46:33,630 --> 00:46:35,160
