615
00:47:36,630 --> 00:47:38,300
Why do you think I ignored you?

616
00:47:38,930 --> 00:47:41,660
It's because I knew you'd get involved.

617
00:47:44,060 --> 00:47:45,330
That's why, Yeo Kyung.

618
00:47:45,660 --> 00:47:46,800
That's why.

619
00:47:48,900 --> 00:47:50,030
Let's do it together.

620
00:47:51,500 --> 00:47:52,600
Let's stop...

621
00:47:53,360 --> 00:47:54,830
running away.

622
00:48:07,460 --> 00:48:08,700
Let's make something clear.

623
00:48:09,600 --> 00:48:11,730
I take the lead. You stay behind me.

624
00:48:11,730 --> 00:48:13,200
Don't do anything alone.

625
00:48:13,960 --> 00:48:16,500
I won't work with you unless you promise me that.

626
00:48:18,400 --> 00:48:19,500
I promise.

627
00:48:23,100 --> 00:48:25,100
There's a secret room in Mr Ha's office.

628
00:48:25,100 --> 00:48:26,930
He uses it to launder cash,

629
00:48:26,930 --> 00:48:28,340
and I found a way to get in.

630
00:48:28,340 --> 00:48:29,700
I'll go in soon.

631
00:48:29,700 --> 00:48:32,000
Get me enough for a search warrant.

632
00:48:32,500 --> 00:48:35,490
I need something concrete. Once we begin,

633
00:48:35,490 --> 00:48:37,860
I'll go after Goongnak Foundation, too.

634
00:48:43,330 --> 00:48:44,760
You should get back to work.

635
00:48:47,800 --> 00:48:48,930
Look after yourself.

636
00:49:08,460 --> 00:49:10,030
Mr Ha.

637
00:49:10,460 --> 00:49:12,130
It's your big day.

638
00:49:12,500 --> 00:49:15,460
Get on Congressman So's good side and fly high.

639
00:49:15,800 --> 00:49:17,600
Take me with you if you can.

640
00:49:17,600 --> 00:49:20,700
Prosecutor Chae Yeo Kyung, was it?

641
00:49:21,460 --> 00:49:23,330
Is she still on that case?

642
00:49:24,230 --> 00:49:26,860
I tied her up for now.

643
00:49:27,660 --> 00:49:29,000
She won't cause any trouble.

644
00:49:42,200 --> 00:49:43,230
Good shot.

645
00:49:44,500 --> 00:49:46,260
Do you work out?

646
00:49:48,200 --> 00:49:49,300
Thank you, Sir.

647
00:49:50,200 --> 00:49:52,330
Your ball goes way farther now.

648
00:50:07,530 --> 00:50:09,800
You hit that too hard.

649
00:50:18,030 --> 00:50:21,310
Prosecutor Ahn, can you go to the toilet?

650
00:50:21,310 --> 00:50:23,880
What for? I just went.

651
00:50:23,880 --> 00:50:24,900
Go again.

652
00:50:27,430 --> 00:50:28,430
Sure.

653
00:50:37,400 --> 00:50:39,160
Congressman Choi told me.

654
00:50:40,760 --> 00:50:42,830
I'd like to invest.

655
00:50:44,930 --> 00:50:46,630
If you take my money,

656
00:50:47,760 --> 00:50:50,300
