657
00:50:51,200 --> 00:50:54,030
No one can touch an investment that my money's in.

658
00:50:55,830 --> 00:50:57,460
Isn't that a strength?

659
00:50:59,200 --> 00:51:02,070
What's the small problem?

660
00:51:02,070 --> 00:51:04,660
I heard it takes a year to launder money.

661
00:51:06,230 --> 00:51:09,430
I'm too impatient to wait that long.

662
00:51:10,160 --> 00:51:12,430
I want it back within three months.

663
00:51:13,530 --> 00:51:15,660
That is the small problem.

664
00:51:16,830 --> 00:51:20,120
