665
00:51:20,120 --> 00:51:21,760
Make it possible.

666
00:51:24,130 --> 00:51:25,700
The motto exists for a reason.

667
00:51:28,200 --> 00:51:31,200
Let's go back to playing golf.

668
00:51:36,100 --> 00:51:37,960
Isn't the weather lovely?

669
00:51:49,530 --> 00:51:52,130
I, Ko Dae Cheon...

670
00:51:55,130 --> 00:51:56,830
have in my name...

671
00:52:09,700 --> 00:52:11,600
Did he make many changes?

672
00:52:12,460 --> 00:52:14,200
It's practically a new will.

673
00:52:16,430 --> 00:52:17,520
Did he mention me in...

674
00:52:17,520 --> 00:52:20,830
I cannot answer any questions right now.

675
00:52:21,660 --> 00:52:23,700
- Mr Park.
 -  I apologise.

676
00:52:24,730 --> 00:52:27,900
I'm obligated to keep everything a secret.

677
00:52:28,730 --> 00:52:29,730
Goodbye.

678
00:52:40,300 --> 00:52:41,300
Mr Park.

679
00:52:41,830 --> 00:52:42,830
Mr Ha.

680
00:52:43,860 --> 00:52:45,260
Why are you here?

681
00:52:46,860 --> 00:52:49,260
