682
00:52:50,530 --> 00:52:51,660
What for?

683
00:52:53,360 --> 00:52:55,700
To write a new will.

684
00:52:58,200 --> 00:52:59,320
I see.

685
00:52:59,320 --> 00:53:01,000
Have a nice day.

686
00:53:43,530 --> 00:53:44,760
You fool.

687
00:53:47,360 --> 00:53:51,130
The mill goes round and round

688
00:53:51,130 --> 00:53:54,430
And round and round

689
00:53:55,330 --> 00:53:57,280
- Come with me.
 -  What for?

690
00:53:57,280 --> 00:53:59,790
