 -  You're so slow.

691
00:53:59,790 --> 00:54:02,600
- We need to leave.
 -  You and your temper.

692
00:54:09,200 --> 00:54:10,680
What are you doing?

693
00:54:10,680 --> 00:54:11,900
You scared me. My goodness.

694
00:54:13,900 --> 00:54:15,030
Are you all right?

695
00:54:16,030 --> 00:54:17,260
Of course I am.

696
00:54:18,460 --> 00:54:19,460
That's good.

697
00:54:22,800 --> 00:54:27,330
I got a little too drunk last night.

698
00:54:28,630 --> 00:54:31,460
