702
00:54:45,380 --> 00:54:46,830
Be there on time.

703
00:54:47,400 --> 00:54:48,530
Mr Ha?

704
00:54:49,530 --> 00:54:50,530
What for?

705
00:54:50,860 --> 00:54:51,960
I don't know.

706
00:54:52,800 --> 00:54:53,830
Bye.

707
00:55:27,530 --> 00:55:28,530
Oh, dear.

708
00:55:29,600 --> 00:55:30,930
Did I wake you?

709
00:55:32,200 --> 00:55:33,260
Sorry.

710
00:55:34,530 --> 00:55:36,660
I meant to come and go unnoticed.

711
00:55:37,460 --> 00:55:39,730
What do you want?

712
00:55:40,130 --> 00:55:42,000
I told you to make things right,

713
00:55:43,200 --> 00:55:44,660
