714
00:55:46,300 --> 00:55:47,500
So this time,

715
00:55:48,600 --> 00:55:50,830
I will make things right.

716
00:55:52,300 --> 00:55:53,930
Wouldn't my shares...

717
00:55:55,830 --> 00:55:58,420
