727
00:58:01,800 --> 00:58:05,530
She will be here soon.

728
00:58:06,460 --> 00:58:10,200
You two can have a lovely chat.

729
00:58:21,600 --> 00:58:23,800
Gil Do.

730
00:58:25,660 --> 00:58:27,530
Kim Gil Do.

731
00:58:48,700 --> 00:58:50,430
No.

732
00:58:53,360 --> 00:58:55,230
This is wrong.

733
00:58:55,900 --> 00:58:57,660
This...

734
00:58:58,130 --> 00:59:01,830
