735
00:59:36,700 --> 00:59:37,800
Follow me.

736
00:59:51,030 --> 00:59:53,030
Myeong, step back.

737
01:00:02,600 --> 01:00:04,830
This is wrong.

738
01:00:06,330 --> 01:00:07,450
This...

739
01:00:07,450 --> 01:00:09,830
Mr Ko. Are you okay?

740
01:00:09,830 --> 01:00:11,520
This is wrong.

741
01:00:11,520 --> 01:00:13,720
Mr Ko. Mr Ko.

742
01:00:13,720 --> 01:00:15,600
You can't...

743
01:00:19,130 --> 01:00:20,930
What?

744
01:00:20,930 --> 01:00:24,300
