748
01:00:36,260 --> 01:00:40,060
Tell me. Did you kill my mother?

749
01:00:45,930 --> 01:00:49,630
Help! Can anyone help us?

750
01:00:50,860 --> 01:00:53,270
Mr Ko. No.

751
01:00:53,270 --> 01:00:55,760
Don't die. You can't die.

752
01:00:56,360 --> 01:00:57,510
Sir!

753
01:00:57,510 --> 01:00:59,140
Oh, no. Mr Ko!

754
01:00:59,140 --> 01:01:03,160
Tell me. Tell me why you killed my mother!

755
01:01:04,960 --> 01:01:06,360
I'm...

756
01:01:07,260 --> 01:01:09,360
