757
01:01:18,300 --> 01:01:19,930
Please don't die. Mr...

758
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:22,100
Mr Ko!

759
01:01:22,760 --> 01:01:23,760
No.

760
01:01:24,260 --> 01:01:25,830
You can't die.

761
01:02:37,660 --> 01:02:40,660
(Master of Revenge)

762
01:03:00,730 --> 01:03:03,430
