768
01:03:17,630 --> 01:03:20,900
I'd like to see Ha Jung Tae being suffocated.

769
01:03:21,430 --> 01:03:23,350
That doesn't mean that I forgive you.

770
01:03:23,350 --> 01:03:25,400
